social_posts.post_text: My First two laps at #Togué since 2018 💪 Would you ride with me here!? I really appreciate the pace and technicality of this track. It's one of the few I've driven that are just as fun driving solo.  Dodging a random #S15 that spun while @cyrusmohebi camera was flopping around was an extra challenge 😳 and @harrisondrifter commentary on the second clip was hilarious 😂 I love @ebisucircuit so much! @lonestardrift @powervehicles100 #ContiShredder
#Dogs of Japan 🐶 don't think I saw a single pup over 15lbs! Which ones you're favorite? Mine is Maddie 😍

#icecream in #Japan 🍦 I've tried so many, eaten too much, and enjoyed every single lick 👅 the best one was the first one that you literally couldn't buy, it was a secret dessert you get at an underground restaurant the chef surprises you with at the end of the meal. Which one looks the best to you?

RAW lap on the togué today chasing @axelfrancoisdriver in his Turbo M50 powered Hyperdrive Interceptor 🚓💨💨💨 I was driving a bit cautious, holding back on the straights and using more hand brake than I usually like but we have 7 more days of drifting ahead of us and this road is unforgiving.  such a fantastic experience thank you @slide_drift_team for hosting the event! 🙏 🇫🇷
Take a ride with me on this insane track! Miranda De Ebro in Spain 🇪🇸 @xtremdrift @axelfrancoisdriver @aisin_europe @leo.ncll

The vibes are on point ☀️ amazing driving, incredible track, fantastic comraderie and some insane media!!! @xtremdrift really made the first stop something special ♥️ huge thank you to everyone involved! 🎥: @maxime_ory @axelfrancoisdriver @automovilclubmirandes

Le dejo mi coche al piloto de hyperdrive @shredderracing y alucino como lo lleva!! Podría decir que mejor que yo!!

Ademas @valvu_motorsport ha podido disfrutar batallando con él!! Incluso nos ha chocado!

Espero verle muy pronto por aquí otra vez!!

HUGE ANNOUNCEMENT! I'm going to be competing in the French Championship next weekend in @axelfrancoisdriver #700HP #GT86 🤘🤘🤘 Such an amazing opportunity to throw down with these dudes I've always dreamed of competing in #Europe 😎 Thank you to Axel and his team for working hard these past few weeks to make this happen. We have a ton of work to do and not much time but we are pushing hard to get it done.  Follow the progress on here and if you are in France come out and watch! #drifting #dreamtrip

Chasing @generation_drift at @naparrak_drift_oficial in @axelfrancoisdriver #Hyperdrive interceptor 🚓💨💨💨 this track is a "Spanish Meihan" but with a bit of elevation and a few different length corners.  I actually enjoyed driving it backwards more! Definitely coming back here ♥️ #meihan #spain #drifting #s13 #E36
Ready for qualifying! Hope it doesn't rain.  Wish me Luck! 💪 @driftcup_mso @axelfrancoisdriver
